00:04:52.560 --> 00:04:54.560
Tu parles comme une vraie dame, aujourd'hui !

00:04:55.770 --> 00:04:58.310
Allons, tiens-toi tranquille, aisa.

00:04:58.560 --> 00:04:59.810
Madame laki !

00:04:59.990 --> 00:05:00.990
Aisa !

00:05:08.450 --> 00:05:10.170
Grand guerrier calgara,

00:05:11.170 --> 00:05:14.420
